flowchart TD
    Start([User Request]) --> Orchestrator[ORCHESTRATOR]
    
    Orchestrator --> Parse[1. Parse Request<br/>Làm sạch & chuẩn hóa]
    
    Parse --> Complexity[2. Complexity Analyzer<br/>Phân tích độ phức tạp]
    
    Complexity --> Decision{Đơn giản?}
    
    %% Simple Path
    Decision -->|Yes| DirectLLM[3. Direct LLM<br/>Trả lời trực tiếp]
    DirectLLM --> FormatSimple[4. Format Response]
    FormatSimple --> Response([Response])
    
    %% Complex Path
    Decision -->|No| Planning[3. Planning Agent<br/>Tạo TODO list]
    
    Planning --> ToolRegistry[4. Tool Registry<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>🔍 Web Search Tool<br/>🤖 LLM Tool<br/>🧮 Calculator Tool]
    
    ToolRegistry --> SelectLoop[5. Tool Selection<br/>Chọn tool cho từng task]
    
    SelectLoop --> ExecuteLoop[6. Execute Tools Sequentially]
    
    ExecuteLoop -->|Task 1| Tool1[🔍 Web Search Tool<br/>Tìm kiếm thông tin trên web]
    ExecuteLoop -->|Task 2| Tool2[🤖 LLM Tool<br/>Phân tích & tổng hợp]
    ExecuteLoop -->|Task 3| Tool3[🧮 Calculator Tool<br/>Tính toán số học]
    
    Tool1 --> Collect[7. Aggregate<br/>Tổng hợp kết quả]
    Tool2 --> Collect
    Tool3 --> Collect
    
    Collect --> FormatComplex[8. Compose Response<br/>Viết lại response]
    
    FormatComplex --> Response
    
    %% Error Handling
    DirectLLM -.->|Error| Retry[Retry hoặc Skip]
    Tool1 -.->|Error| Retry
    Tool2 -.->|Error| Retry
    Tool3 -.->|Error| Retry
    Retry -.-> ExecuteLoop
    
    %% Styling
    style Orchestrator fill:#FFE5E5,stroke:#FF6B6B,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Complexity fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1976D2,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Decision fill:#E5F9FF,stroke:#00BCD4,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style DirectLLM fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Planning fill:#FFF3E0,stroke:#F57C00,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style ToolRegistry fill:#FFE0B2,stroke:#FB8C00,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style SelectLoop fill:#E1F5FE,stroke:#03A9F4,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style ExecuteLoop fill:#E8EAF6,stroke:#5C6BC0,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Tool1 fill:#E1F5FE,stroke:#03A9F4,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Tool2 fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#AB47BC,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Tool3 fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
